                                        <li>South Indian names (180+)</li>
                                        <li>Eastern region names (90+)</li>
                                        <li>Western region names (80+)</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <h6>Name Categories:</h6>
                                    <ul class="feature-list">
                                        <li>Traditional names</li>
                                        <li>Modern variations</li>
                                        <li>Cultural significance</li>
                                        <li>Regional specialties</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a href="#" class="btn-custom btn-primary-custom">
                            <i class="fas fa-database me-1"></i>Explore New Names
                        </a>
                    </article>

                    <!-- Tournament Feature News -->
                    <article class="news-card fade-in">
                        <span class="news-badge badge-development">In Development</span>
                        <h2 class="news-title">Tournament Mode & Leaderboards System</h2>
                        <div class="news-meta">
                            <span><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt me-1"></i>November 20, 2024</span>
                            <span><i class="fas fa-user me-1"></i>Game Design Team</span>
                            <span><i class="fas fa-tags me-1"></i>Multiplayer, Competition</span>
                        </div>
                        <img src="/images/VocaVerse3.png" alt="AI Opponent" class="news-image">
                        <div class="news-content">
                            <p>Competitive players, rejoice! We're developing a comprehensive tournament system that will allow players to compete in organized competitions with rankings, rewards, and seasonal challenges.</p>

                            <div class="timeline mt-4">
                                <div class="timeline-item">
                                    <h6>Phase 1: Basic Tournament Structure</h6>
                                    <p>Single-elimination and round-robin formats with automated matchmaking.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-item">
                                    <h6>Phase 2: Leaderboard Integration</h6>
                                    <p>Global and regional leaderboards with ELO rating system.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-item">
                                    <h6>Phase 3: Rewards & Achievements</h6>
                                    <p>Unlock badges, titles, and special privileges through competitive play.</p>
                                </div>
